Docs:
    • <a>content</a> → content can be plain text, img, ...
    - Attributes:
      • href(hypertext reference) → url, link, relative path, absolute path(/root-level)
                                  → can be e.g file, img, another html, external url,...  
                                  → #: To link top of the page
                                  → #id: To link to an element with given identifier!
                                  → "mailto:...": Mail client will open with pre-filled given email address
      • download → boolean attribute, instead of seeing link, we download it!
      • target="_blank" → to open link in a new tab
      